Package: NEONiso
Type: Package
Title: Calibrate and plot NEON Atmospheric Isotope Data
Version: 0.3
Author: Rich Fiorella
Maintainer: Rich Fiorella <rich.fiorella@utah.edu>
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: This package provides functions for downloading,
    calibrating, and analyzing NEON data, with a particular focus
    on the atmospheric isotope and eddy covariance data.
